                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090626-12-off66 t18090626-12-cd67"></join>, a watch, value 2 l. a watch key, value 3 d. and a pair of shoes, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090626-12-victim152" type="victimName">
